
Quick steps to build FastJetClustering:
---------------------------------------

    - FastJetClustering depends on the following packages:
        LCIO GEAR Marlin ROOT FastJet and CMake
        
        if you have access to /afs/desy.de/ then you will find all this packages
            (EXCEPT FastJet) under:

            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/i386_gcc34_sl4/   # SL4 32bit
            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/i386_gcc41_sl5/   # SL5 32bit
            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/x86_64_gcc41_sl5/ # SL5 64bit

    - Follow this steps to configure/build FastJetClustering using /afs/desy.de :
        
        mkdir build ; pushd build
        
        # initialize ilcsoft
        . /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/<YOUR_ARCHITECTURE>/<ILCSOFT_VERSION>/init_ilcsoft.sh

        # ------ build FastJet ----------------------------------------------
        wget "http://www.lpthe.jussieu.fr/~salam/fastjet/repo/fastjet-2.4.2.tar.gz"
        tar xzf fastjet-*gz
        pushd fastjet-*/
        ./configure --prefix=$PWD/../fastjet
        make && make install
        popd
        # -------------------------------------------------------------------

        # ------ build FastJetClustering ------------------------------------
        cmake -C $ILCSOFT/ILCSoft.cmake -DFastJet_DIR=$PWD/fastjet ..
        make install
        popd
        # -------------------------------------------------------------------


        # ------ load FastJetClustering into Marlin -------------------------
        export MARLIN_DLL=$MARLIN_DLL:$PWD/lib/libFastJetClustering.so
        Marlin -x > mysteer.xml  # should include FastJetClustering


